{
  "texts": [
    "And indeed, this seems to be exactly the case. 9",
    "Consider, for example, the data gathered by Skjuvie and colleagues (Skjuve et al. 2021).",
    "Through a series of semistructured interviews, they investigated the relationship between regular users of Replika and their avatars.",
    "Crucially, no participant mentioned their avatar being felt as a part of themselves.",
    "Indeed, when asked about how they would feel if their avatars were to disappear, participants typically reported only that they would feel sad."
  ]
}